Subject: Re: Too many IF's!
In-Reply-To: <199507210828.SAA02320@yallara.cs.rmit.edu.au>
Message-Id: <Pine.HPP.3.91.950722121658.12103B-100000@nyquist.ee.ualberta.ca>
