>    Function: Typefile(Fastcallport,Filename)
>                             d0       a1
> 
>    Offset : -114
> 
>             Well I call this function like this:
> 
>   Lib open 5,"fastcall.library",0     >>> This suxx !!
>   tx$="HELLO! HERE ON FASTCALL SCREEN!"
>   tx$=tx$+chr$(0)
